item.description: Head of Engineering at Continuum Economics, having fun & rapidly building product & tooling using PHP7, Python, Javascript, Laravel, & Vue. When not working you can find me at a variety of meetups (Node, Vue), hiking, reading, and enjoying life (✈️, 🍻, 🌮).
